## Workspace Rules

### Shared vs Owned Areas

| Area | Ownership | Rules |
|------|-----------|-------|
| `docs/architecture/` | Collaborative | Any agent can contribute |
| `docs/reference/` | Collaborative | Any agent can contribute |
| `docs/guides/` | Collaborative | Any agent can contribute |
| `docs/plans/` | Collaborative | Any agent can contribute |
| `lib/docs/` | Collaborative | Tool docs co-located with source |
| `tools/` | Open | Agents can freely add standalone utilities |
| `lib/` | Shared modules | Coordinate changes — don't edit unilaterally |

